  "detailed_description": "<strong>Meow Legion </strong>is a game about assembling an army of cats to defend against waves of enemies.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>I made this game because I like cats.</strong><br></li><li><strong>controller</strong> recommended.<br></li><li>Left mouse button/RT to <strong>shoot</strong>.<br></li><li>Right mouse button/LT to <strong>recall</strong> cats.<br></li><li>Recall allows your cats to defend for you and <strong>pick up items</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/642c2ffcd1de6f27dafc696023268c18.poster.avif?t=1711995359\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/642c2ffcd1de6f27dafc696023268c18.webm?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/642c2ffcd1de6f27dafc696023268c18.mp4?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Total 10 types of cats<br></li><li>You get stronger every time you lose. You will receive a random <strong>meow card</strong>, each with different attribute bonuses for each cat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/643c11d915b15170ec1c0d2270953469.poster.avif?t=1711995359\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/643c11d915b15170ec1c0d2270953469.webm?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/643c11d915b15170ec1c0d2270953469.mp4?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Please don't forget to carry a <strong>meow card</strong>. In the interface shown below, you can select the meow card you wish to carry into battle. Each cat can only carry one meow card per battle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/d025c878fb3ff619d8d17127bf64c819.poster.avif?t=1711995359\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/d025c878fb3ff619d8d17127bf64c819.webm?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/d025c878fb3ff619d8d17127bf64c819.mp4?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Upgrade your cat cards: There are three levels of cat cards, and the higher the level, the more attribute boosts you get. You can <strong>level up</strong> by merging them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/a4e5773d62f6ff14dc1c1b0bdff92744.poster.avif?t=1711995359\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/a4e5773d62f6ff14dc1c1b0bdff92744.webm?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/a4e5773d62f6ff14dc1c1b0bdff92744.mp4?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
